messages.messageBody:
Hello Everyone,

I too like this group and it has helped even though I just joined. Tyra said it so perfectly! On another note I have never built a chat group or have been a monitor. I was just discussing with my dh how much work is involved in reading and approving the posts. WOW! I am very pleased and excited to read the post here. It seems to be a more gentle group than others I have joined.

smiles~hugs~Angela

OH I FORGOT is anyone on this list in Kentucky? We are traveling to Lexington, Winchester & Staton on Wednesday thru Sunday from Michigan. ;o)
